# Licenses

This project is licensed under different licenses for its software code and its data/content.

## Cinema Database (Data)
The cinema screen size database (`public/screens-db.json` and `src/features/database/screens-db.json`) contains data sourced and derived from **LF Examiner** (https://lfexaminer.com/theaters/).

As of March 1, 2025, LF Examiner content is released under the **Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial-ShareAlike 4.0 International License (CC BY-NC-SA 4.0)**.

In compliance with the ShareAlike (SA) and Attribution (BY) terms of this license:
* **Attribution**: You must attribute the data to LF Examiner (https://lfexaminer.com/theaters/).
* **NonCommercial**: You may not use this data for commercial purposes.
* **ShareAlike**: Any remix, transformation, or derivative work built upon this data must be distributed under the same CC BY-NC-SA 4.0 license.

Therefore, the database files in this repository are licensed under **CC BY-NC-SA 4.0**.

For the full license terms, please visit:
https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/

